# AI Financial Assistant

An AI-powered financial assistant built using **Google ADK, Gemini, FastAPI, PostgreSQL, and SQLAlchemy**. The system enables users to manage expenses, create budgets, analyze spending patterns, and generate financial summaries through natural language conversations.

## Features

* User Authentication using JWT
* Expense Tracking through natural language
* Budget Creation and Management
* Budget Summary Generation
* Spending Analysis and Insights
* Google Gemini-powered intent understanding
* Google ADK multi-tool agent architecture
* PostgreSQL database integration
* REST APIs with FastAPI
* Swagger API documentation

## Tech Stack

### Backend

* Python
* FastAPI
* SQLAlchemy
* PostgreSQL (Supabase)

### AI & Agent Framework

* Google Gemini API
* Google ADK (Agent Development Kit)

### Authentication

* JWT Authentication
* Password Hashing

